more than I can bear.

01:12.500 --> 01:13.540
My pastor.

01:13.550 --> 01:14.730
We had an affair.

01:14.760 --> 01:17.920
And this is one of the letters
he wrote while we were together.

01:17.960 --> 01:19.050
I loved him.

01:19.060 --> 01:20.120
