01:20.140 --> 01:21.720
I want to sue him.

01:21.740 --> 01:23.340
–Clarence.
–Yes.

01:23.350 --> 01:24.120
This is Maureen.

01:24.160 --> 01:25.350
She loves her pastor.

01:25.390 --> 01:29.350
Clarence will help you. Pay no
attention to his shifty eyes.

01:31.130 --> 01:32.540
Hello.

01:32.550 --> 01:34.710
–Who are you?
–Who are you?

01:35.040 --> 01:35.610
Busy.

01:35.620 --> 01:36.590
Andrea, hi.

01:36.600 --> 01:38.580
My friends call me the “beav”.

01:38.970 --> 01:39.770
Uh, oh, yes. I remember you.

01:39.810 --> 01:41.900
You're the one that sued
over the nuclear power plant.

01:41.940 --> 01:44.730
Well, what is it today, Beav?

01:45.780 --> 01:46.960
Congratulations.

01:46.970 --> 01:48.470
Who's the lucky troop ship?

01:48.510 --> 01:50.170
